*[[帛琉|帛琉]]：0.01%

===中亞===
*[[吉爾吉斯|吉爾吉斯]]：0.05%<ref name=BAC>{{cite web|url =http://apps.who.int/gho/data/view.main.54600|title =Legal BAC limits by country|publisher =[[World_Health_Organization|World Health Organization]]|accessdate =21 February 2015|ref =none|archive-date =2015-02-19|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150219221459/http://apps.who.int/gho/data/view.main.54600|dead-url =no}}</ref>
