== 法律责任 ==
: <small>主條目：{{le|各國醉酒駕駛法律|Drunk driving law by country}}</small>

泰國2016年4月立法規定酒駕跟交通違規累犯都要到[[太平間|太平間]]服勞役<ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20160413/37160532/ |title=泰國嚇阻酒駕罰進太平間洗屍 |date=2016年4月13日|newspaper=台灣蘋果日報|author=韓政燕|access-date=2017-03-07|archive-date=2017-03-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170307204043/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20160413/37160532/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url = http://englishnews.thaipbs.or.th/drunk-drivers-now-must-clean-hospital-morgues-observe-real-action-emergency-rooms/ |title = Drunk drivers now must clean hospital morgues, observe real action at emergency rooms |date=June 21, 2016 |publisher=Thai PBS Reporters|location=Thailand |access-date=2017-03-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170307123749/http://englishnews.thaipbs.or.th/drunk-drivers-now-must-clean-hospital-morgues-observe-real-action-emergency-rooms/ |archive-date=2017-03-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，美國加州罰酒駕累犯洗[[屍體|屍體]]以及18,000美元<ref>{{cite web |url = https://www.cdc.gov/motorvehiclesafety/pdf/impaired_driving/drunk_driving_in_ca.pdf |title = Sobering Facts: Drunk Driving in California |publisher=CDC, USA|access-date=2017-03-07|archive-date=2019-02-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190212063532/https://www.cdc.gov/motorvehiclesafety/pdf/impaired_driving/drunk_driving_in_ca.pdf |dead-url=no}}</ref>罰款。[[臺北市|臺北市]]議員[[何志偉|何志偉]]參考兩國相關刑責，正式於質詢中提出「累犯洗大體」的懲罰方案，讓酒駕者到殯儀館服社會勞動役、體驗生命教育，讓酒駕者了解生命無常，造成雙方的不幸，徒增社會成本。實際實作酒駕受罰民眾前往殯儀館協助清洗「大體進出室」，但不會碰觸到大體，以尊重大體為原則。<ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=186148|title=罰款無嚇阻作用！議員提仿效國外　酒駕就「洗大體當懲罰」|date=2016-09-30 |publisher=三立新聞 |author1=李品誼 |author2=姜毅宏|access-date=2017-03-07 |archive-date=2017-03-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170319205942/http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=186148 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2016/10/03/2003656431|title= No to morgue duty for repeat DUI offenders: Ko |date=2016-10-03|publisher=The Taipei Times|author1=Ho Shih-chang|author2=Liang Pei-chi|access-date=2017-03-07|archive-date=2020-01-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200116195414/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2016/10/03/2003656431 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。台灣首例於2017年3月16日由[[臺灣臺東地方檢察署|台東地檢署]]正式安排，十名酒駕累犯的社會勞動人前往台東市殯葬管理所，清洗遺體冰櫃、解剖台等周遭設備<ref>{{cite news |url = https://udn.com/news/story/7315/2344911 |title = 全台首例 酒駕累犯罰洗大體冰櫃 |date=2017-03-16 |newspaper=[[聯合報|聯合報]] |author=羅紹平|access-date=2017-05-04 |archive-date=2019-12-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191216194215/https://udn.com/news/story/7315/2344911 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=233903 |title = 遭罰洗大體冰櫃　台東10酒駕累犯：會怕啊，不敢再喝了 |date=2017-03-16 |publisher=[[三立新聞|三立新聞]] |access-date=2017-05-04 |archive-date=2017-07-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170704233253/http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=233903 |dead-url=no}}</ref>

